* For dialing-only text entry *

* As for all implementations of {@link KeyListener}, this class is only concerned * with hardware keyboards. Software input methods have no obligation to trigger * the methods in this class.

* The characters that are used.

     * @see #getAcceptedChars

methods.name: protected int lookup(KeyEvent event, Spannable content)
methods.comment:
* Overrides the superclass's lookup method to prefer the number field
     * from the KeyEvent.

methodNames: protected int lookup(KeyEvent event, Spannable content)
